'''Akosua''' yɛ a edin a wɔde to mmaa a wɔ woo wɔn kwasiada <ref>(PDF) The Sociolinguistic of Akan Personal Names (researchgate.net)</ref> <ref>Akan names and their meanings - YEN.COM.GH</ref>. Afoforo dwen sɛ Asantefoɔ  na ɛtɔ saa din yi nanso, saa adeyɛ yi yɛ nea ɛkɔ so wɔ akanfoɔ nyinyaa  (akanfoɔ  ne Asantefoɔ, Akuapemfoɔ, Akyemfoɔ, Fantefoɔ) a wodi ammerɛ so. Onipa biara wɔ su ne nneyɛe bi a ɛda adi wɔ da wɔde woo no. Akosua mmerane ne Dampo a n'asekyerɛ ne nea ne  ho yɛ hare. Enti, ɔbaa biara a wɔ woo no kwasiada no yɛ nea ɛse sɛ ne ho yɛ hare wɔ bibiara mu.

== Farebae ne nkyerɛase ==
Wɔ Akanfoɔ amammerɛ mu no, wonya din a wɔde to da biara no firii wɔn ahoni  hɔ. Wonyaa edin Akosua firii Ahoni a ne hɔ twa a ɛyɛ Kwasiada no ho. Mmaa a wɔ woo wɔn kwasiada no yɛ nea wɔyɛ akandifo wɔ wɔn mpɔtam anaa obue kwan. Wɔyɛ mfeefeemu na won ani tumi gye nneɛma a ɛho hia ho.

== Mmaa ahorɔw ==
Sɛnea wɔkyerɛw Edin a wɔde to nna wɔ Ghanaman mu no gu ahorɔw .Eyi te saa esiane akuo ahorɔw a ɛwɔ akanfoɔ mu no ni. Akanman kuo biara wɔ sɛnea wɔkyerɛw edin no, anaa nsonsonoeɛ nnim. Akuapemfoɔ  ne Asantefoɔ kyerɛw Akosua, na Mfantefoɔ kyerɛw no Esi.

== Marima ==
Wɔ Akanfoɔ ne afoforo ammmerɛ a ɛwɔ Ghanaman mu no, nna din a wɔto yɛ nea ɛba mienu; mmaa ne mmaraima. Edin a wɔde to ɔbabirima a wɔ woo no Kwasiada no ne Kwasi anaa akwasi.

== Atitriw a wokura saa Edin no ==
Ghanafo mma ahorɔw pii no ara kura wɔn amammerɛ din na afei nso, abrɔfo anaa Akristofoɔ din. Atitriw a wokuara saa din no bi ne;

* Akosua Addae Amoo Ghanani Agodie mu nsɛmkyerɛwni
* Akosua Gyamama Busia  Ghanani siniyɛfo
* Akosua Serwaa Ghanaiani Mirikatuni<ref name=":4" />
* Akosua Frema Osei Opare Ghanani Amanyɔni
* Rebecca <nowiki>''Becca''</nowiki> Akosua Acheampomaa Acheampon, Ghanani nnwomtoni, nnwomkyerɛwni, ne siniyɛfo

